#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.gamma"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a Gamma distribution."
msgstr "从 Gamma 分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:3 of
msgid ""
"Samples are drawn from a Gamma distribution with specified parameters, "
"`shape` (sometimes designated \"k\") and `scale` (sometimes designated "
"\"theta\"), where both parameters are > 0."
msgstr ""
"样本从具有指定参数的 Gamma 分布中抽取，`shape`（有时记为 \"k\"）和 `scale"
"`（有时记为 \"theta\"），这两个参数都大于 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:7 of
msgid "The shape of the gamma distribution. Should be greater than zero."
msgstr "Gamma 分布的形状参数。应大于零。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:9 of
msgid ""
"The scale of the gamma distribution. Should be greater than zero. Default"
" is equal to 1."
msgstr "Gamma 分布的尺度参数。应大于零。默认值为 1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:12 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``shape`` and ``scale`` are both scalars. Otherwise, "
"``np.broadcast(shape, scale).size`` samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状为，例如 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本"
"。如果 size 为 ``None``（默认），当 ``shape`` 和 ``scale`` 都为标量时返回"
"单个值。否则，抽取 ``np.broadcast(shape, scale).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:17 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的 chunk 大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:19 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:21 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:24 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized gamma distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的 Gamma 分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`scipy.stats.gamma`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:30 of
msgid ""
"probability density function, distribution or cumulative density "
"function, etc."
msgstr "概率密度函数、分布函数或累积密度函数等。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:33 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:34 of
msgid "The probability density for the Gamma distribution is"
msgstr "Gamma 分布的概率密度为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:36 of
msgid ""
"p(x) = x^{k-1}\\frac{e^{-x/\\theta}}{\\theta^k\\Gamma(k)},\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:38 of
msgid ""
"where :math:`k` is the shape and :math:`\\theta` the scale, and "
":math:`\\Gamma` is the Gamma function."
msgstr ""
"其中 :math:`k` 是形状参数，:math:`\\theta` 是尺度参数，:math:`\\Gamma` 是"
" Gamma 函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:41 of
msgid ""
"The Gamma distribution is often used to model the times to failure of "
"electronic components, and arises naturally in processes for which the "
"waiting times between Poisson distributed events are relevant."
msgstr ""
"Gamma 分布通常用于建模电子元件的失效时间，并在泊松分布事件之间的等待时间"
"相关的自然过程中出现。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:46 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:47 of
msgid ""
"Weisstein, Eric W. \"Gamma Distribution.\" From MathWorld--A Wolfram Web "
"Resource. http://mathworld.wolfram.com/GammaDistribution.html"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:50 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Gamma distribution\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gamma_distribution"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:54 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

