msgid "Draw samples from the distribution:"
msgstr "从分布中抽取样本："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.gamma.gamma:62 of
msgid ""
"Display the histogram of the samples, along with the probability density "
"function:"
msgstr "显示样本的直方图以及概率密度函数："

